<div class="commenttext">

Hi!  Once I learned how to do this I love it.  I work in Adobe Photoshop Elements<br />
open your file <br />
use your magnetic tool outline the image you want to have color. (this takes practice)<br />
Then choose "select" from your file menu, then choose "inverse"<br />
then choose "enhancements", choose adjust color and then choose remove.  and there you have it.  <br />
<br />
Good luck!

