<span class="smalltext">
2003-11-07 13:37:13&nbsp;<!-- begin conditional display of username -->

<a href="http://www.oreillynet.com/pub/au/54">Derrick Story</a> | <a href="http://oreilly.com/badges.html" target="popup" onclick="javascript:window.open('http://oreilly.com/badges.html', 'popup', 'width=300, height=300');"><img title="O'Reilly Author" src="/images/badge_author.gif" alt="O'Reilly Author" width="14" height="14" style="padding-right:5px;margin-bottom:-3px;" /></a><!-- 1 --><a href="http://oreilly.com/badges.html" target="popup" onclick="javascript:window.open('http://oreilly.com/badges.html', 'popup', 'width=300, height=300');"><img title="O'Reilly Blogger" src="/images/badge_blogger.gif" alt="O'Reilly Blogger" width="14" height="14" style="padding-right:5px;margin-bottom:-3px;" /></a>


