if you use Macromedia Fireworks MX and go through this route File\Export there should be steps to save your image at web quality. Also, there is a function through this route to specify the file size which you want. <br />
If you use microsoft photo editor and go to save as, select .jpg then click on the "more" button and select the quality manually. 50-70% is good enough.

