I would agree that in the second photo with the cloudy wb setting the color went magenta.  However, in different shots with different cameras, this may help a lot.  In the second shot with the poloarizer, it also went magenta.  Did you change the wb setting with this photo?  It could be that the glasses weren't a neutral grey.  <br />
